  "cards": [
    {
      "dot": "cyan",
      "title": "当前支持路径",
      "items": [
        "briefloop run 只创建并启动 runtime handoff，不在 Python 内生成整份简报",
        "Hermes、Claude、OpenCode、Operator 为支持路径；Codex 与 CodeBuddy 仍属实验路径"
      ]
    },
    {
      "dot": "emerald",
      "title": "权威边界",
      "items": [
        "Agent 负责理解、委派、起草和建议；不能直接推进 stage、通过 Gate 或批准交付",
        "Python 事务是状态、事件、冻结、Gate、Finalize 与 Delivery 事实的唯一写者"
      ]
    },
    {
      "dot": "violet",
      "title": "只读投影",
      "items": [
        "Quality Panel、provenance 与 report bundles 读取权威事实，但不是 release authority",
        "Semantic Evaluator 是独立 offline-shadow 实验，不进入正常 run、QP、Gate 或交付"
      ]
    },
    {
      "dot": "amber",
      "title": "迁移状态",
      "items": [
        "ControlStore v2、intake_v2 与 core_run_v2 已合并，但仅由隐藏 CLI 驱动且没有 active consumer",
        "PR-4B 与 public authority cutover 尚未成为 origin/main 的当前运行能力"
      ]
    }
